00:46:54.612 --> 00:46:55.909
you have to parse cookie data.

980
00:46:56.458 --> 00:46:56.797
And there,

981
00:46:56.798 --> 00:46:59.300
there was always a mixture of bytes and Unicode.

982
00:46:59.681 --> 00:47:01.501
And it was very easy to work with on Python 2,

983
00:47:01.623 --> 00:47:04.244
and it was incredibly annoying to work on Python 3,

984
00:47:04.326 --> 00:47:05.447
at least initially.

985
00:47:06.346 --> 00:47:11.072
